Reno Omokri, has opined that there is no man that can resist a woman sexual temptation. In his words, he said, the man that can resist a womans sexual temptation has not being born. Read what he wrote below, “Dear men, When Joseph was accosted by Potiphar’s wife, he did not fast, or pray, or sing psalms. He fled. Don’t be foolish. The man that can resist sexual temptation has NOT been born. Unless she is your wife, never be alone with a woman in a room with a bed! In fact, if you can even avoid being alone with a woman other than your wife, all the better. When you got born again, your spirit received power. But that power did not extend to a particular part of your body. If it sees what it likes, it becomes hungry. Therefore, don’t create the atmosphere for it to become hungry for evil food!”  In 2022, Avoid Women Who Want To Spend Your Money With You –… Sound Sultan Was An Uncommon Man-Reno Omokri Hails Late Musician